Default request-response scheme

input:
    user id
        2 bytes
    state
        viewAngle
            2 bytes
        isMoting
            1 byte
        motionAngle
            2 bytes
        shooting
            1 byte


output:
    users
        count of users
            2 bytes
        user 1
            user id
                2 bytes
            user type
                2 bytes
            x-coord
                int part
                    2 bytes
                fractional part
                    1 byte
            y-coord
            health
                1 byte
            state
        ...
        user n
    bullets
        count of bullets
            2 bytes
        bullet 1
            author id
                2 bytes
            bullet type
                2 bytes
            bullet distance
                1 byte
            x-coord
                int part
                    2 bytes
                fractional part
                    1 byte
            y-coord
        ...
        user n




